  volume    =  163,
  number    =  12,
  pages     =  124113,
  abstract  = "We present a variant of the approximate second order
               coupled-cluster method (CC2) with a two-parameter size-consistent
               Brillouin–Wigner (BW-s) partitioning instead of a Møller–Plesset
               (MP) partitioning for the unperturbed Hamiltonian, which we refer
